1、Fastfile内容：

APP_NAME  = "xxx"//APP名
WORKSPACE = "xxx.xcworkspace"//workspace管理则需加该行
SCHEME = "xxx"//工程名
OUTPUT_DIRECTORY = "/Users/Joe/Desktop/Archive/xxx"//ipa路径
IPA_NAME = "xxx"//ipa名称
EXPORT_METHOD = "enterprise"

default_platform(:ios)

platform :ios do
  desc "Description of what the lane does"
  lane :to_firim do // to_firim 为名字，可任意
	cocoapods
	gym(
	scheme: "#{SCHEME}",
	export_method: "#{EXPORT_METHOD}",
	output_directory: "#{OUTPUT_DIRECTORY}",
	output_name: "#{IPA_NAME}",
	)
	xcclean(
		workspace: "#{WORKSPACE}",
		scheme: "#{SCHEME}"	
	)
	firim(firim_api_token:"xxxxxxxx")//自动上传fir
  end
end

2、需注意，项目使用了pod管理第三方，添加的cocoapods 需在Gemfile中同步添加 gem "cocoapods";
3、保存之后，终端输入 fastlane ios to_firim 
